[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在安卡希雅离开那间小小的漫画屋之后，我再也没能在心流内景中找到她的意识映射。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一般而言，这种情况说明她已经沉入了最深层的意识空间，将在那里与最后的枷锁对抗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然剩下的路只能靠她自己走下去，但在定下那个约定之后，我对她能打破暗示这件事，怀着十足的信心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_01",
        "zh_CN": "你保证，等我去到未来那一天，一定会见到你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我保证。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在离开心流内景、黏腻的感觉渐渐退却后，我首先感知到的，是现实世界里舒爽的风和暖暖的阳光，还有一个带着些许得意的笑声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_02",
        "zh_CN": "嘿嘿~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "睁开眼，安卡希雅正温柔地凝视着我。但此刻的她，却不是之前娇小的模样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她明显长高了很多，灰色的长发几乎垂到腰际。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "战术套装也随着她的变化而自动重构，流畅的线条完美贴合着她现在的身形。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过，虽然姿态变得成熟了，安卡希雅的气质却还是和以前一模一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "见我一直盯着她看，她反而有些不好意思起来，下意识地用手拨了拨垂落的长发，眼神有些闪躲。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你这是在打破枷锁的过程中，完全掌握了“相变核心”的力量？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_03",
        "zh_CN": "嗯~是这样没错啦，算是个意外收获吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_04",
        "zh_CN": "之前我总是有些抗拒“变化”，所以无意识地拒绝了战术套装的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_05",
        "zh_CN": "这种想法，倒是和瑟茜施加给我的心理暗示意外重合了，于是这次就一起解决掉了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_06",
        "zh_CN": "你是不是应该夸夸我呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "厉害厉害，不愧是我的安卡希雅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我伸出手想要像往常一样揉揉她的脑袋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但按照惯性抬起手后，手掌却停留在少女胸口的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她注意到我的动作，噗嗤一声笑了出来，然后主动低下头，像小猫一样钻进我的掌心，轻轻蹭了蹭。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_07",
        "zh_CN": "快点问问我是怎么做到的~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "安卡希雅是怎么做到的？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女脸上的笑意依旧，但眼神却渐渐变得认真起来，带上了几分郑重。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_08",
        "zh_CN": "在和分析员告别之后，我又在心流内景里停留了很久很久，像一个旁观者一样，重新走过了那些已经消失的日子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_09",
        "zh_CN": "我抗拒“变化”，并不是因为旧时代真的有多美好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_10",
        "zh_CN": "真正令我感到害怕的，是时代消亡后，我被一个人孤零零地留了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_11",
        "zh_CN": "所以，为了证明自己并不孤单，我努力和旧时代建立联系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_12",
        "zh_CN": "甚至想过，如果连我都变了，那旧时代真的什么都不剩了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_13",
        "zh_CN": "但说到底……我只是不想自己一个人罢了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周围的风似乎都静止了，她的脸颊微微泛红，却没有移开视线，就那样认真地、专注地看着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_14",
        "zh_CN": "所以，我想说的是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_15",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，谢谢你爱我，也谢谢你一直陪伴着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_16",
        "zh_CN": "停留在哪个时代，对我来说已经不重要了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_17",
        "zh_CN": "因为我只想去往有你的未来，就像我们约定的那样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说完，她再次伸出手来，小指微微弯曲，眼睛里闪烁着期待的光芒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伸出手",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "两根小指轻轻相触，然后慢慢收拢，紧紧地勾住彼此。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就这样，我们在“另一个时代”将承诺闭环。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "约定化作一根看不见的红线，将我们牢牢系在了一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然后，她习惯性地高高踮起了脚尖，却发现自己的唇停留在了我的鼻尖上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_18",
        "zh_CN": "诶？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_19",
        "zh_CN": "哈哈，条件反射，条件反射，忘了现在不需要踮这么高了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她微微调整了角度，将柔软的唇精准地贴了上来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "时间仿佛在这一刻静止，彼此的温度在舌间传递。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "直到瑟茜小跑而来的脚步声响起，才将我们拉回现实。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_sexi_01",
        "zh_CN": "主管，安卡希雅，你们已经……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "大安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl001_20",
        "zh_CN": "已经打破心理暗示了哦，崇福街的居民应该也能陆续醒过来了吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_sexi_02",
        "zh_CN": "居然真的做到了吗？这也太不可思议了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对了。瑟茜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "茉莉安呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "环顾四周却没见到茉莉安的身影，而瑟茜则支支吾吾地组织起语言。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_sexi_03",
        "zh_CN": "就在几分钟之前，我们遇到了苏菲……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "三分钟前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "打开心流内景后的安卡希雅就像是睡着了一样，安静地坐在长凳上，单手托着自己的脑袋，呼吸平稳而绵长。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但瑟茜却是一副愁容满面的样子，眉毛几乎要拧在了一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安幽潮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl005_01",
        "zh_CN": "放心吧，分析员和安卡希雅会顺利回来的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "茉莉安的语气倒是意外地轻松，和瑟茜的焦虑形成了鲜明的对比。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_sexi_04",
        "zh_CN": "为什么……你这么笃定呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安幽潮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl005_02",
        "zh_CN": "你不觉得，相信是一种很奇妙的力量吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_sexi_05",
        "zh_CN": "嗯？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安幽潮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl005_03",
        "zh_CN": "因为有人相信你，为了不辜负那个人的期待，你就会想要努力做些什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安幽潮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl005_04",
        "zh_CN": "如果那份相信是独一无二、是只属于你的，那么它带来的力量就会变得更加强大。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说这话时，茉莉安的眼神和语气都变得柔软起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安幽潮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_girl005_05",
        "zh_CN": "我和安卡希雅都是这样。因为不想让分析员失望，所以我们都会拼尽全力去做到。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep8_sexi_06",
        "zh_CN": "是……是这样吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟茜若有所思地点点头，似乎第一次尝试理解这种可以支撑彼此的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
